  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/2c569454d10ab9494ea094f4c94fcea7.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/2c569454d10ab9494ea094f4c94fcea7.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/2c569454d10ab9494ea094f4c94fcea7.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/c96801f30c69f1c12d07387fb7561e74.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/c96801f30c69f1c12d07387fb7561e74.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/c96801f30c69f1c12d07387fb7561e74.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As New York falls under attack by mysterious creatures, <strong>you and your team of 1 to 8 fearless journalists must risk everything to snap spectacular photos and escape to make the headlines</strong> ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/1f1114b861e082b04d73ad66da9f6f24.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/1f1114b861e082b04d73ad66da9f6f24.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/1f1114b861e082b04d73ad66da9f6f24.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/b7c9a2ba91a2fe94180812152e3cd940.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/b7c9a2ba91a2fe94180812152e3cd940.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/b7c9a2ba91a2fe94180812152e3cd940.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the abandoned & dangerous streets of New York, enter buildings, search every dark alley and hidden corner for anything that could be worth discovering. Danger is around every turn.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/a1a6ce8142aa71a36b1e0df45ccbd308.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/a1a6ce8142aa71a36b1e0df45ccbd308.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/a1a6ce8142aa71a36b1e0df45ccbd308.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/9e33b5244f1cafd5cb383b620e3bc3ad.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=594 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/9e33b5244f1cafd5cb383b620e3bc3ad.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/9e33b5244f1cafd5cb383b620e3bc3ad.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each member of your team is armed with a camera. Snap shots of the destruction, the alien invaders, or even your teammates being torn apart by creatures. The choice is yours—capture the chaos however you see fit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/656671fdce56dadc19c431e763a334e0.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=102 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/656671fdce56dadc19c431e763a334e0.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/656671fdce56dadc19c431e763a334e0.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/6f054d5fea2d531155cecc86ee3df106.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/6f054d5fea2d531155cecc86ee3df106.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/6f054d5fea2d531155cecc86ee3df106.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you survive the chaos and make it out alive, review your photos and hope they’re headline-worthy. You start with 3 press cards, and each expedition uses one. Only by making the headlines can you earn more and continue your dangerous journey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/226765728b5edf27b7975d482cd7baba.avif?t=1761229580\" width=684 height=64 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/2c569454d10ab9494ea094f4c94fcea7.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/2c569454d10ab9494ea094f4c94fcea7.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/2c569454d10ab9494ea094f4c94fcea7.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/c96801f30c69f1c12d07387fb7561e74.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/c96801f30c69f1c12d07387fb7561e74.webm?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/c96801f30c69f1c12d07387fb7561e74.mp4?t=1761229580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As New York falls under attack by mysterious creatures, <strong>you and your team of 1 to 8 fearless journalists must risk everything to snap spectacular photos and escape to make the headlines</strong> ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/1f1114b861e082b04d73ad66da9f6f24.poster.avif?t=1761229580\" width=600 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059070/extras/1f1